                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5724" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0861</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9316 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">一元买壳，是福是祸？国资海科金入主金一文化上演反向混改</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A blessing or a curse to buy shell for one yuan? State-owned Haikejin took over Jinyi Culture and staged a reverse mixed reform</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许金花，张浣铃</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京金一文化发展股份有限公司，北京海淀科技金融资本控股集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国有资本；并购动因；股权质押；纾困；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">State-owned capital, M&amp;A motivation, Equity pledge, Bail out</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近几年来，国家大力推进混合所有制改革，出台多项政策鼓励国有资本入股非国有企业，上演反向混改。而诸多民营上市公司股权质押严重，难以维持企业的生存和发展，急需外界纾困，因此寻找资金充足的国资接盘成为众多民企的选择，并掀起了“国资入主潮”。本案例描述了在反向混改背景下，国资海科金入主民营上市公司金一文化的过程。金一文化由于财务状况恶化、股权质押严重导致公司资金链紧张，原控股股东将其股权一元转让给拥有国资背景的海科金集团，实际控制人变更为海淀区国资委。那么一元买壳的背后原因是什么？国资的纾困效果又如何？通过剖析这一案例，引导学员关注国有资本收购民营上市公司，重点引导学员关注国资助力上市公司纾困这一形式，同时可以让学生更好地了解国资入主民企的动因及效果。
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, the state has vigorously promoted the reform of mixed ownership, and has issued a number of policies to encourage state-owned capital to buy shares in non-state-owned enterprises, and staged a reverse mixed reform. However, many private listed companies have serious equity pledges, which make it difficult to maintain the survival and development of the company and urgently need external relief. Therefore, finding a well-funded state-owned asset has become the choice of many private enterprises, and set off a &quot;state-owned capital influx&quot;. This case describes the process of state-owned Haikejin taking over the private listed company Jinyi Culture under the background of the reverse mixed reform. Due to the deterioration of the financial situation and the serious pledge of equity, the company’s capital chain was strained. The original controlling shareholder transferred his equity by one yuan to the Haikejin Group, which has a state-owned background, and the actual controller was changed to the Haidian District State-owned Assets Supervision and Administration Commission. So what is the reason behind buying shells for one yuan? How effective is the relief of state-owned capital? Through the analysis of this case, the students are guided to pay attention to the state-owned capital acquisition of private listed companies, and the focus is to guide the students to pay attention to the relief of listed companies with state-funded power. At the same time, students can better understand the motivation and effect of state-owned capital entering private enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《资本运营》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国有资本纾困民营上市公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
